      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我走出公司大楼，拿出手机找到那位女士的号码并拨打过去。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "ChatGPT5.5",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_032",
      "target_id": "sent_006",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "电话接通后，她笑着询问打电话的人是谁。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "ChatGPT5.5",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_033",
      "target_id": "sent_007",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我笑着告诉她是我，并邀请她晚上一起见面。",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "ChatGPT5.5",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_034",
      "target_id": "sent_008",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "她在电话中确认了见面的时间，我很高兴地答应了。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "ChatGPT5.5",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_035",
      "target_id": "sent_009",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "最后，她在电话里做出 OK 的手势，并开心地表示没有问题。",
      "confidence": 0.94,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "ChatGPT5.5",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_036",
